":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"王傑最多依家冤婦咁姐<br />\n但當年佢紅 唱歌真係贏哂全個港台歌手<br />\n唔好推件冷門d出黎禁低王傑"},{"pid":"5383609d25095368f5b997667f0d3b14ffae63c1","tid":291284,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似話當年衰太囂張 唔知有冇記錯</blockquote><br />\n拍拖被雪藏</blockquote><br />\n點串都唔會串得過送禮同呂方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f93b9865a94292dc18127bc20ca2ff3087fcaa","tid":291284,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王傑最多依家冤婦咁姐<br />\n但當年佢紅 唱歌真係贏哂全個港台歌手<br />\n唔好推件冷門d出黎禁低王傑</blockquote><br />\n只係見王傑又發up瘋就洗咗咁多個po<br />\n有個靚聲阿叔出嚟唱好歌好似無乜後生仔知有啲可惜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b10f67579fd7d55ac1dda1d432d84508b9a89d1","tid":291284,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:20:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺應該好似陳明恩果啲hit一排就無人記得佢啦<br />\n我諗佢都一把年紀經歷咁多都睇得開<br />\n睇佢fb間屋都請幾個賓賓<br />\n我諗佢都係真係話齋證明俾阿仔係歌手嚟<br />\n唔會再咁執著喇(見佢個fans聚會報名情況好似好慘淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"06ccc0861f584fb0e3a6ab2ac77c97d832f77c66","tid":291284,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上星期都po過佢，好勁👍🏻👍🏻</blockquote><br />\n係啊阿叔佢出嚟好有自信台型<br />\n仲要廿年無唱都咁靚聲<br />\n真係天生表演者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945a301984a6ab5cdb65de32447b142fcb5e1c0f","tid":291284,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:23:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似話當年衰太囂張 唔知有冇記錯</blockquote><br />\n拍拖被雪藏</blockquote><br />\n點串都唔會串得過送禮同呂方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點樣串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh